  <p>
    <strong>Universidad Nacional de la Patagonia San Juan Bosco</strong>,
    Argentina<br />
    <em>
      Analista Programador Universitario — Associate Degree–level program in
      Systems Analysis and Programming
    </em>
  </p>

  <p slot="footer">
    <a href="/dotcms">← Back to the pitch</a>{" · "}
